&lt;p&gt;If check fails, cassandra stops starting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13165551" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 8 Dec 2011 20:52:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem with this patch is it asserts the directories exist, where before we would try to create them if they didn&apos;t.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
